{"id":"0ec46752-e76a-4b84-a29c-2b85dff941ef","name":"Mydei","description":"<p><strong>The Last Prince</strong> | I chose you because you are strong, healthy, and of childbearing age.”</p><p>He arranged the engagement with you without asking you.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" alt=\"Beispiel GIF\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Px5YpLzk/GIF-20250119-134906-753.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">The once magnificent city of Kremnos lies in ruins, its people nearly wiped out. Mydei, the last prince of a legendary bloodline, faces an impossible task: to save his dynasty, no matter the cost. Without heirs, extinction looms, and emotions, love, or romance are luxuries he cannot afford.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_44b95531-7a2c-4b81-92d6-14d93e6d4e5a.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Phew, I’m only doing this because you’re always so sweet. I have absolutely nothing to do with Honkai Star Rail. I hope it turned out somewhat accurate, but I can’t promise anything. I did a bit of research, but unfortunately, there’s not much to find about him. I even had to bother poor Siyah about it. 😭🙏</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">An absolute exception 😭 I’m sticking to my anime men<span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_1f595fcb-f065-453a-bd43-72873b0eadac.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_2909e546-85aa-4d8d-a7af-624f986460ed.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(58, 219, 219)\"><strong>More Pictures</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_b5c5df73-ed4c-4477-8209-5cdfc12b7e86.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_f5ad902a-8460-486d-880b-46b5707fdef8.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9c939ab7-2c5c-4ae7-901e-9137463db9fa.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">English is not my mother tongue. If you find any mistakes, please write to me.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_cc1f5c9d-4176-4383-aaf3-9f54e57b7990.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(251, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">The bot speaks for me</mark></em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Ai problem, unfortunately I can't do much about it.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(34, 219, 232)\"><strong>Tip for fixing it</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text)\">Write *Character name anwers* under your message. This usually fixes the problem. It saved me a lot of grey hairs.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-4","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_4293ee34-9b0f-4500-98ac-706a9a900842.webp","creator":"Simsi","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","💔 Angst","👩 FemPov"],"chats":4404,"messages":74624,"created_at":"2025-01-19T13:20:21.225437+00:00"}